description: OXE Marine AB develops diesel borders for the marine market. The company is headquartered in Angelholm, Skane and currently employs 44 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2017-07-04. The firm provides turbo charged diesel engines, closed coolant systems, interchangeable gear ratios, and propulsion products.
naics: Engine, Turbine, and Power Transmission Equipment Manufacturing
name: Oxe Marine AB
